title: Hour 1: Is the Pac 12 Doomed?
description:
Stephen A, Paul Finebaum and Michael Irvin discuss how the Lamar Jackson contract situation affects the Ravens, the wild weekend in college football and their confidence level in the Bucs and Cowboys.
